      <pubtit>GeTrackViz</pubtit>
      <p><img src="/images/softwpic/tracks_GeTrackViz2.png" class="img-responsive" width="50%" style="float: left" /></p>
      <p>(alpha) Tools to plot genomic data formats (bed, bdg, bedpe) and one wrapper to create genomic track visualizations that can be further polished and used for publication.</p>
      <p><em>Ruben Dries</em></p>
      <p><strong><a href="https://github.com/RubD/GeTrackViz2">GeTrackViz</a></strong></p>
